# ZKBA artifact output directory marker (Phase O3-ZKBA-TRACK1 Stream Z3)
#
# Compiled artifacts (HTML + manifest.json) live in subdirectories:
#   gic_continuity_ledger/<input_commitment_hex>.html
#   gic_continuity_ledger/<input_commitment_hex>.manifest.json
#
# Compiled output is deterministic from inputs (vsd_ui_compiler.compile_artifact)
# and excluded from git via frontend/.gitignore (src/artifacts/*/).  This
# .gitkeep file ensures the parent directory is tracked even when no
# artifacts are present.
